.SH NAME
flits_to_desc \- returns the num of Tx descriptors for the given flits
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "unsigned int" flits_to_desc
.BI "(unsigned int n "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "n" 12
the number of flits

Returns the number of Tx descriptors needed for the supplied number
of flits.
